g.text: gz目录(gz Directory):包含各个镜像的所有镜像层gz包
(All image layer GZ packets containing each image)
images目录(images Directory):包含各个镜像的镜像层解压后的目录及
对应的配置文件(Contains the image layer of each image after
decompression directory and Corresponding configuration file)
db目录(db Directory):镜像相关metadata存储目录,采用sled数据库
(Image related metadata storage directory, using sled database)
